Entries.Wed6: Yesterday with Dr. Jacob was awesome. I helped Dr. Jacob deliver a calf!#$b#Well, mostly I just handed him stuff, but it was pretty exciting... and a bit gross too!$1
Entries.summer_Wed6: Dr. Jacob had to euthanise an injured bull yesterday. He was pretty upset about it.#$b#I was a bit too. I guess we city kids don't really think about where meat comes from.
Entries.fall_Wed6: Phew. Don't tell Mom, but I'm a bit sore today. Dr. Jacob and me captured some sick sheep.#$b#They're tougher than they look! We managed to save almost all of them though.$1
Entries.winter_Wed6: Vet work is really hard ... and cows can be mean. But it's interesting too.#$b#Way more interesting than accountancy.
